ntralasien, sondern er verdeutlicht auch die generellen Strukturdefizite von Politik in Zeiten der Globalisierung.  aThe Politics of the Periphery tells of the conditions for political struggle in times of globalization, and the constant pressure to simulate modern conditions.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aKirgistan. 4aKulturanthropologie. 4aPolitik. 4aPolitikwissenschaft. 4aPolitische Soziologie. 4aProtest. 4aSystemtheorie. 4aZivilgesellschaft. 4aÖffentlichkeit. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / Cultural & Social.2bisacsh  aCivil Society.  aCultural Anthropology.  aKyrgyzstan.  aPolitical Science.  aPolitical Sociology.  aPolitics.  aProtest.  aPublic Sphere.  aSystems Theory.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2015z9783110438741oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839431436zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839431436423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839431436/original  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DSWb2015  aZDB-23-TGPc2014d2016